Docker --help
  |
  -> Docker run --help          //help regarding parameters available under "run" command
Docker info
Docker version
Docker -v                       // Brief version info 
___________________________________________________
commands for containers
--------------------------------------------------
Docker create                   // create own container
Docker pull                     // pull container from hub.docker.io
Docker push                     // push changes to hub.docker.io
Docker ps                       // List all process running in docker
Docker ps -a                    // show all containers which is being executed & also shows info about the containers
Docker rm                       // remove particular container from docker
Docker stop <container ID>      // stops the current executing containers
Docker images                   // shows all the images available locally
